{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <i>Horde Together</i>, the undead never rest! Face off against endless waves of zombies in this pulse-pounding co-op experience. Work together to hold your ground, repair your getaway vehicle, and outlast the undead hordes to secure your escape!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Choose your Character:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from one of many unique characters, each with their own backstory and abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/CharacterSelectionGIF.gif?t=1733801535\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Fight the Undead:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight waves off waves of zombies and other horrifying creatures, all well keeping yourself and your friends alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/FightingGIF01.gif?t=1733801535\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Repair your Vehicle:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Scour the map for the missing pieces required to repair your broken down vehicle, each component being one step closer to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/CarRepairGIF.gif?t=1733801535\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Escape with your Life:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Once your vehicle is repaired and in working order, load up with your friends and escape before being overwhelmed by the endless hordes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Beware there might not always be a spot on board for every person..\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2-6 Player online coop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">8+ Playable character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2